entities.rdfs:label: AllDifferent
entities.rdfs:comment: The class of collections of pairwise different individuals.

entities.rdfs:label: AllDisjointClasses
entities.rdfs:comment: The class of collections of pairwise disjoint classes.

entities.rdfs:label: AllDisjointProperties
entities.rdfs:comment: The class of collections of pairwise disjoint properties.

entities.rdfs:label: Annotation
entities.rdfs:comment: The class of annotated annotations for which the RDF serialization consists of an annotated subject, predicate and object.

entities.rdfs:label: AnnotationProperty
entities.rdfs:comment: The class of annotation properties.

entities.rdfs:label: AsymmetricProperty
entities.rdfs:comment: The class of asymmetric properties.

entities.rdfs:label: Axiom
entities.rdfs:comment: The class of annotated axioms for which the RDF serialization consists of an annotated subject, predicate and object.

entities.rdfs:label: Class
entities.rdfs:comment: The class of OWL classes.

entities.rdfs:label: DataRange
entities.rdfs:comment: The class of OWL data ranges, which are special kinds of datatypes. Note: The use of the IRI owl:DataRange has been deprecated as of OWL 2. The IRI rdfs:Datatype SHOULD be used instead.

entities.rdfs:label: DatatypeProperty
entities.rdfs:comment: The class of data properties.

entities.rdfs:label: DeprecatedClass
entities.rdfs:comment: The class of deprecated classes.

entities.rdfs:label: DeprecatedProperty
entities.rdfs:comment: The class of deprecated properties.

entities.rdfs:label: FunctionalProperty
entities.rdfs:comment: The class of functional properties.

entities.rdfs:label: InverseFunctionalProperty
entities.rdfs:comment: The class of inverse-functional properties.

entities.rdfs:label: IrreflexiveProperty
entities.rdfs:comment: The class of irreflexive properties.

entities.rdfs:label: NamedIndividual
entities.rdfs:comment: The class of named individuals.

entities.rdfs:label: NegativePropertyAssertion
entities.rdfs:comment: The class of negative property assertions.

entities.rdfs:label: Nothing
entities.rdfs:comment: This is the empty class.

entities.rdfs:label: ObjectProperty
entities.rdfs:comment: The class of object properties.

entities.rdfs:label: Ontology
entities.rdfs:comment: The class of ontologies.

entities.rdfs:label: OntologyProperty
entities.rdfs:comment: The class of ontology properties.

entities.rdfs:label: ReflexiveProperty
entities.rdfs:comment: The class of reflexive properties.

entities.rdfs:label: Restriction
entities.rdfs:comment: The class of property restrictions.

entities.rdfs:label: SymmetricProperty
entities.rdfs:comment: The class of symmetric properties.

entities.rdfs:label: Thing
entities.rdfs:comment: The class of OWL individuals.

entities.rdfs:label: TransitiveProperty
entities.rdfs:comment: The class of transitive properties.

entities.rdfs:label: allValuesFrom
entities.rdfs:comment: The property that determines the class that a universal property restriction refers to.

entities.rdfs:label: annotatedProperty
entities.rdfs:comment: The property that determines the predicate of an annotated axiom or annotated annotation.

entities.rdfs:label: annotatedSource
entities.rdfs:comment: The property that determines the subject of an annotated axiom or annotated annotation.

entities.rdfs:label: annotatedTarget
entities.rdfs:comment: The property that determines the object of an annotated axiom or annotated annotation.

entities.rdfs:label: assertionProperty
entities.rdfs:comment: The property that determines the predicate of a negative property assertion.

entities.rdfs:label: backwardCompatibleWith
entities.rdfs:comment: The annotation property that indicates that a given ontology is backward compatible with another ontology.

entities.rdfs:label: bottomDataProperty
entities.rdfs:comment: The data property that does not relate any individual to any data value.

entities.rdfs:label: bottomObjectProperty
entities.rdfs:comment: The object property that does not relate any two individuals.

entities.rdfs:label: cardinality
entities.rdfs:comment: The property that determines the cardinality of an exact cardinality restriction.

entities.rdfs:label: complementOf
entities.rdfs:comment: The property that determines that a given class is the complement of another class.

entities.rdfs:label: deprecated
entities.rdfs:comment: The annotation property that indicates that a given entity has been deprecated.

entities.rdfs:label: differentFrom
entities.rdfs:comment: The property that determines that two given individuals are different.

entities.rdfs:label: disjointUnionOf
entities.rdfs:comment: The property that determines that a given class is equivalent to the disjoint union of a collection of other classes.

entities.rdfs:label: disjointWith
entities.rdfs:comment: The property that determines that two given classes are disjoint.

entities.rdfs:label: distinctMembers
entities.rdfs:comment: The property that determines the collection of pairwise different individuals in a owl:AllDifferent axiom.

entities.rdfs:label: equivalentClass
entities.rdfs:comment: The property that determines that two given classes are equivalent, and that is used to specify datatype definitions.

entities.rdfs:label: equivalentProperty
entities.rdfs:comment: The property that determines that two given properties are equivalent.

entities.rdfs:label: hasKey
entities.rdfs:comment: The property that determines the collection of properties that jointly build a key.

entities.rdfs:label: hasSelf
entities.rdfs:comment: The property that determines the property that a self restriction refers to.

entities.rdfs:label: hasValue
entities.rdfs:comment: The property that determines the individual that a has-value restriction refers to.

entities.rdfs:label: imports
entities.rdfs:comment: The property that is used for importing other ontologies into a given ontology.

entities.rdfs:label: incompatibleWith
entities.rdfs:comment: The annotation property that indicates that a given ontology is incompatible with another ontology.

entities.rdfs:label: intersectionOf
entities.rdfs:comment: The property that determines the collection of classes or data ranges that build an intersection.

entities.rdfs:label: inverseOf
entities.rdfs:comment: The property that determines that two given properties are inverse.

entities.rdfs:label: maxCardinality
entities.rdfs:comment: The property that determines the cardinality of a maximum cardinality restriction.

entities.rdfs:label: minCardinality
entities.rdfs:comment: The property that determines the cardinality of a minimum cardinality restriction.

entities.rdfs:label: onClass
entities.rdfs:comment: The property that determines the class that a qualified object cardinality restriction refers to.

entities.rdfs:label: onDataRange
entities.rdfs:comment: The property that determines the data range that a qualified data cardinality restriction refers to.

entities.rdfs:label: onDatatype
entities.rdfs:comment: The property that determines the datatype that a datatype restriction refers to.

entities.rdfs:label: onProperties
entities.rdfs:comment: The property that determines the n-tuple of properties that a property restriction on an n-ary data range refers to.

entities.rdfs:label: onProperty
entities.rdfs:comment: The property that determines the property that a property restriction refers to.

entities.rdfs:label: oneOf
entities.rdfs:comment: The property that determines the collection of individuals or data values that build an enumeration.

entities.rdfs:label: priorVersion
entities.rdfs:comment: The annotation property that indicates the predecessor ontology of a given ontology.

entities.rdfs:label: propertyChainAxiom
entities.rdfs:comment: The property that determines the n-tuple of properties that build a sub property chain of a given property.

entities.rdfs:label: propertyDisjointWith
entities.rdfs:comment: The property that determines that two given properties are disjoint.

entities.rdfs:label: qualifiedCardinality
entities.rdfs:comment: The property that determines the cardinality of an exact qualified cardinality restriction.

entities.rdfs:label: sameAs
entities.rdfs:comment: The property that determines that two given individuals are equal.

entities.rdfs:label: someValuesFrom
entities.rdfs:comment: The property that determines the class that an existential property restriction refers to.

entities.rdfs:label: sourceIndividual
entities.rdfs:comment: The property that determines the subject of a negative property assertion.

entities.rdfs:label: targetIndividual
entities.rdfs:comment: The property that determines the object of a negative object property assertion.

entities.rdfs:label: targetValue
entities.rdfs:comment: The property that determines the value of a negative data property assertion.

entities.rdfs:label: topDataProperty
entities.rdfs:comment: The data property that relates every individual to every data value.

entities.rdfs:label: topObjectProperty
entities.rdfs:comment: The object property that relates every two individuals.

entities.rdfs:label: unionOf
entities.rdfs:comment: The property that determines the collection of classes or data ranges that build a union.

entities.rdfs:label: versionIRI
entities.rdfs:comment: The property that identifies the version IRI of an ontology.

entities.rdfs:label: versionInfo
entities.rdfs:comment: The annotation property that provides version information for an ontology or another OWL construct.
